					>
						It's the reason why a local asset is not the same as a workshop published asset.
					</p><p class="mt-4">For local assets: filename.Asset Name_Data<br />For published workshop assets: SteamID.Asset Name_Data</p>
				</div><div class="lg:w-1/3">
					<a href="/images/asset/building/prefab.jpg" target="_blank">
						<ResponsiveImage
							src={images.prefab}
